thread.title: Stephanie Freed
thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by Stephanie Freed

author: Stephanie Freed
title: Stephanie Freed
text: The product is excellent. The Salmon is the best I have tasted. However, the shipping is questionable. The packaging material was warm by the time I got home. The product was still frozen so I did not complain but on my last order the product was no longer frozen. I did complain and they told me they would not send it the same way next time. I am concerned about this type of packaging.
